{"tid":2123990,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人喺條街度行會一邊行一邊屌鬼","createTime":"2020-07-25T05:27:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-25T06:43:38.000Z","uid":360404,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bd7a5c0be97ab6da613169fdd80e4e2690a5c534","tid":2123990,"uid":360404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T05:27:42.000Z","msg":"香港夏天天氣賤種到仆街，跟住仲要多屏風樓，又熱又哂<br />\n又焗，再加上今年要戴個濕尻口罩攪到更加辛苦<br />\n同埋你一戴左口罩之後就會好唔想爆汗，好唔想整濕個口罩，咁樣既情況下會令到個人更撚加燥<br />\n我有喺條街度行真係會燥到忍唔住大大聲自言自語喺度屌鬼：<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"small\">嘩乜撚野天氣黎架</span></span><span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">屌你老母</span></span><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">屌你老母</span></span><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">屌你老母</span></span><br />\n跟住成條街既人望哂過黎"},{"pid":"ab1a6d73c075bae34af759f13c2c12fd3aa9462e","tid":2123990,"uid":89064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T05:42:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a04b7d80778e9c30e3f5d04f4818e63dadd6f39c","tid":2123990,"uid":272202,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T05:46:18.000Z","msg":"原來係你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲以為係白卡佬"},{"pid":"e212abb6caba0fb79c5e0917eec586c001fcd421","tid":2123990,"uid":251510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T05:50:57.000Z","msg":"同意 推"},{"pid":"2f5b45cf685ec10f803f27e6c5ac7e49f7fb223b","tid":2123990,"uid":308450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T05:53:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ee8259d4a7a56d12781d1314ea3f05497781953d","tid":2123990,"uid":239270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T05:54:11.000Z","msg":